"I consider this project to be to be, quite literally, my life saver. The project has only reached his stage with a ton of unselfish help from my friends and ex-colleagues from business. Their efforts ranged notably from capable ‘pro bono’ work in marketing and strategy to funding my manuscripts and art.My friends and I sincerely believe this project will enjoy great success! Now, with their funds exhausted, I need help from the wider public to break through with this project.See below what we offer... Please also read my own tragic story at the very end of this appeal."Norbert Voss '13 Sensual Confessions’ is a creative, winning concept primed and ready for your funding: Entertaining, erotic tales illustrated by a contemporary artist working closely with an intuitive author to capture the true essence of what has passed, or what is destined to come to pass!Captured are true-life romantic episodes and experiences of so-called ‘Muses’, women that have opened their hearts, no, their very souls, and shared their sensual secrets with the author, Norbert Voss. These authentic records have been documented in his colorful, captivating, and rich writing style and are impatiently awaiting closer scrutiny by a wide audience. The tales are of varying length and erotic intensity. The ‘Muses' Comments’ at the end of the stories are both amusing and engaging, while the ‘Author’s Comments’ are quite insightful.All stories are illustrated by Hardy Laddey, a renowned German artist.Preview the small art sample contained in the image gallery above. View thefull complement of illustrations and enjoy the free sample chapter on 13sensusualconfessions.infoYou’re also warmly invited to visit the Author’s Page on Amazon here.  It’s not a niché market. It’s the mainstream: The Romantic-Erotica Genré commands over 40% market share of profitable publications.And ’13 Sensual Confessions’ is poised to occupy a respectable share within that abundant domain! Anonymous interviews with a 100-strong focus group were extremely encouraging. Indeed, most trial readers testified: They adore the book, both the words, and the art!Reader Testimonials are overwhelming:“The combination of Voss’ texts, Laddey’s pictures, and the Muses’ descriptions has an effect on women comparable to the effect of Viagra on men.” (Julianne Voss-Pamplin, Australia, the author´s 74-year-old mother)
“The troika of eyewitness reports, words and images, leaves the connoisseur alternating between feeling a state of speechlessness and being irresistibly breath taken.” (Joshua Kruse, USA, Member of the Focus Group, Homemaker, Teacher of his Homeschooled Kids) “The ’13 Sensual Confessions’ is a real appetizer and an inspiration for making one’s own fantasies evolve into realities.” (Anonymous, Member of the Focus Group) High praise indeed, which demands a thorough examination by lovers of the romantic-erotic genre.Do you remember ‘Picture Books’?Many focus group readers affirmed they share the author's love of illustrated books. Do you remember listening to your Kindergarten teacher reading to you? Do you remember when she turned the book around to show you and your classmates the colorful pictures? Wasn’t it magnetic? Would you now, as an adult, like to relive that magnetism? You can turn back time!Wrapped between the covers of ’13 Sensual Confessions’ is a fascinating ‘picture book’ for grown-ups.  Originally, only the hardcover, the 'Collector's Edition', was advance printed and tested. It is a very weighty book due to the exceptional quality of the pages.Our research clearly showed, while readers loved the book, more flexibility would provide for increased market success. Dividing the ‘Collection’ into two, lighter and less cumbersome 'Volumes' was the first logical amendment to the format.Strong recommendations from our test readers were to have the book made available electronically. This was not only due to reading convenience, but also, readers felt a stronger sense of privacy was needed when consuming ’13 Sensual Confessions’ on public transport.The so-called Unit Tree in the below figure demonstrates a product range to satisfy all preferences while paying tribute to all wallet sizes.  Immediate goals include publishing ’13 Sensual Confessions’ as follows:
As eBooks - divided into five Selections and the Volumes One and Two on November 1st, 2016;
As Paperback Editions - divided into Volume One and Two, in both in full-color and black & white (economy edition) on December 1st, 2016;
As the complete 550-page-plus ‘Collector’s Edition’ - in impeccable hardcover quality also on December 1st, 2016
 Short and Medium-term goals include:
Translating the complete series into German and subsequently launching the book on this absolutely key market for the erotic genre.
Completing the screenplay of '13 Sensual Confessions'.

After establishing consistent cashflow through sales, further translations will include Spanish, French, and Italian;
Thereafter, an expansion with translations to Japanese and Chinese is foreseen.
 Going Forward: 
A new set of stories for a 'Next Collection' by the Voss-Laddey Duo has been defined. To be commissioned after the successful launch of the first 'Collection';
Further publications with other exciting duos are presently in the advanced planning stages; 
Also, a  wide range of merchandise is certainly conceivable to benefit from the anticipated success ‘13 Sensual Confessions’.
 We believe we’re a strong, effective, efficient, and extremely creative group. Our individual track records speak volumes.The market is competitive. We’re extraordinarily competitive, too, though. We aren’t poled to lose. We love to win!We’re prepared! We have the products to be well represented in a highly competitive market. aMuse has a mission, and we have a plan.Could we fail? Yeah, failure is in play ~ as it always is. Is the aMuse Team infallible? What/who is? However, each of us has faced and beaten adversity: We are stronger for it. Your benevolent contribution will expedite a successful, global launch of this noteworthy product range potentially facilitating joy and enticing, memorable hours for lovers of the romantic-erotic genre. With your support, we’ll implement. All we need to win is you!The real challenge for self-publishers today is getting noticed in a true avalanche of eBooks and the creators need funding to energize efforts in this arena. With their own resources dried, the creators need a new seed to finance a breakthrough. To secure global exposure and expand the products into new languages, USD 100,000 is being sought for:
Financing the inventory of the first English print editions in both paperback and hardcover: 20,000 USD;
Strategic, international marketing of the eBooks and printed books on Amazon and various other popular eBook outlets and platforms in key markets: 30,000 USD;
Financing the German translation: 30,000 USD;
Launch & Marketing in Germany 10.000 USD;
Various administrative costs (ISBN, legal, copyright, travel, office supplies, etc.): 10,000 USD.
